metadata.name: World of Yin & Yang: Aloof
metadata.description:
"Aloof" from "World of Yin & Yang" is one among the 8 part conceptual photo series.

World of Yin & Yang is an ancient concept that talks about the two complementary forces that make up all aspects of life. This here is a rendition of Yin & Yang conceptualised through character, juxtaposition of colour, and elements, viewed through a series of photographs.

Photography NASEEF GAFOOR  
Talent MEDINA & NASTYA  
Costume stylist SIKHA SIVAKUMAR  
Words THAYYIBA JINAN  
Post production SANOOP EC
